        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#oliverioDAI1"/>, p. 93, n. <citedRange>21</citedRange></bibl>, whence
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>9.22</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>012400</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, p. <citedRange>164</citedRange> (date), pp. <citedRange>297-298</citedRange>, number 38 (text)</bibl>.</p> 
                    <p>Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#laronde1987"/>, pp. <citedRange>103-104 and 117</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
                    <p>For a general bibliography on the accounts of the damiergoi see <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr011400</ref>.
                </p>
